value: Ne me tirez pas de ce rêve !
This outfit is so colorful! It's not well suited to spying... Er, I mean, it's kind of conspicuous.
Shh! Look how close they are! You're going to ruin it!
Tout d'abord, je ferai rêver un héros... et ensuite un autre... Et ils commenceront à éprouver des sentiments... Et puis... Et puis ! Oooh !
If only I really had the power to give people dreams! *sigh*
Ne le dites pas à mon père ! Il ne peut pas me voir habillée ainsi !
I guess it's not so bad to dress up now and again! *giggle*
I appreciate the gift, but there's no need to butter me up. I already love the Order of Heroes!
